*mpir-1.3.1-r1 (09 Apr 2010)

  09 Apr 2010; Christopher Schwan <cschwan@students.uni-mainz.de>
  +mpir-1.3.1-r1.ebuild:
  Fixed executable stacks in new revision

  26 Mar 2010; François Bissey <f.r.bissey@massey.ac.nz> mpir-1.3.1.ebuild:
  keywording ~ppc

  22 Feb 2010; François Bissey <f.r.bissey@massey.ac.nz> mpir-1.3.1.ebuild:
  Make the dependency on yasm on x86/amd64 olnly. This will allow testing on
  other arch.
  Also fixed a typo, the ebuild is not under "atack" anymore. 

*mpir-1.3.1 (20 Feb 2010)

  20 Feb 2010; François Bissey <f.r.bissey@massey.ac.nz>
  -mpir-1.3.0.ebuild, +mpir-1.3.1.ebuild:
  revbump of mpir. Changed nocxx to cxx.

  29 Jan 2010; François Bissey <f.r.bissey@massey.ac.nz>
  -mpir-1.3.0_rc3.ebuild, -mpir-1.3.0_rc6.ebuild, +mpir-1.3.0.ebuild,
  +files/mpir-1.3.0-ABI-multilib.patch, +files/mpir-1.3.0-yasm.patch,
  -files/mpir-1.3.0_rc3-ABI-multilib.patch,
  -files/mpir-1.3.0_rc3-yasm.patch:
  bumping to 1.3.0 release, removed old rc

*mpir-1.3.0_rc6 (15 Jan 2010)

  15 Jan 2010; Christopher Schwan <cschwan@students.uni-mainz.de>
  +mpir-1.3.0_rc6.ebuild:
  Version bump

  28 Nov 2009; Christopher Schwan <cschwan@students.uni-mainz.de>
  mpir-1.3.0_rc3.ebuild, +files/mpir-1.3.0_rc3-ABI-multilib.patch:
  Added a tentative patch to avoid conflict between gentoo's ABI and
  mpir's ABI - this patch renames ABI to MPIRABI similar to the patch
  from dev-libs/gmp

  22 Nov 2009; François Bissey <f.r.bissey@massey.ac.nz>
  mpir-1.3.0_rc3.ebuild, -files/mpir-1.3.0_rc3-fix-yasm-path.patch,
  files/mpir-1.3.0_rc3-yasm.patch:
  consolidated and slightly edited the yasm patches - sync with science
  overlay so changed cxx flag to nocxx.

  20 Nov 2009; Christopher Schwan <cschwan@students.uni-mainz.de>
  mpir-1.3.0_rc3.ebuild:
  Injected -m64 FLAG, which hopefully resolves amd64 issue

  20 Nov 2009; Christopher Schwan <cschwan@students.uni-mainz.de>
  mpir-1.3.0_rc3.ebuild, +files/mpir-1.3.0_rc3-fix-yasm-path.patch:
  Added fix to correctly call yasm on amd64

*mpir-1.3.0_rc3 (15 Nov 2009)

  15 Nov 2009; François Bissey <f.r.bissey@massey.ac.nz>
  +mpir-1.3.0_rc3.ebuild, -mpir-1.3.0.ebuild,
  +files/mpir-1.3.0_rc3-yasm.patch, +metadata.xml:
  correct version, add flag for fat binaries, patch to use portage provided
  yasm, metadata.xml added

*mpir-1.3.0 (06 Nov 2009)

  06 Nov 2009; Christopher Schwan <cschwan@stamaonline.de> +mpir-1.3.0.ebuild:
  Initial import

